# 🛒 Product Backlog – Online Store

## 📌 Overview
This product backlog defines the key features and user stories for a varied online store. It is organized by epics, user stories, and priority levels following Scrum methodology.

---

## 🔝 Epics
- User Experience (UX/UI)
- Product Catalog
- Payments & Checkout
- Shipping & Logistics
- Marketing & Promotions
- Security & Trust
- Administration

---

## 📋 User Stories

### 🧑‍💻 User Experience (UX/UI)
- **US01**: As a customer, I want to easily navigate the store so I can find products quickly.
- **US02**: As a customer, I want an attractive design so I feel confident shopping.
- **US03**: As a customer, I want to search products by name or category to save time.

---

### 🛍️ Product Catalog
- **US04**: As a customer, I want to see clear product images to make better decisions.
- **US05**: As a customer, I want detailed descriptions to understand what I am buying.
- **US06**: As a customer, I want to see product availability to avoid confusion.

---

### 💳 Payments & Checkout
- **US07**: As a customer, I want multiple payment methods (card, transfer, etc.) to choose the most convenient.
- **US08**: As a customer, I want a fast checkout process to save time.
- **US09**: As a customer, I want to see the final total before paying to avoid surprises.

---

### 🚚 Shipping & Logistics
- **US10**: As a customer, I want to know shipping costs before paying.
- **US11**: As a customer, I want to track my order to know when it will arrive.
- **US12**: As a customer, I want different delivery options to choose the best one.

---

### 📢 Marketing & Promotions
- **US13**: As a customer, I want to see offers and discounts to save money.
- **US14**: As a customer, I want personalized recommendations.
- **US15**: As a customer, I want to save products to a wishlist.

---

### 🔐 Security & Trust
- **US16**: As a customer, I want my data to be secure so I can shop safely.
- **US17**: As a customer, I want to see reviews from other users to trust the product.

---

### 📊 Administration
- **US18**: As an admin, I want to easily add products.
- **US19**: As an admin, I want to update prices and stock.
- **US20**: As an admin, I want to see sales reports.

---

## ⚡ Prioritization (MVP)

### 🔥 High Priority
- US01: Easy navigation  
- US03: Product search  
- US04: Product images  
- US05: Product descriptions  
- US07: Payment methods  
- US08: Fast checkout  
- US09: Order total visibility  
- US10: Shipping costs  
- US16: Data security  

---

### ⚖️ Medium Priority
- US06: Stock visibility  
- US11: Order tracking  
- US13: Promotions  
- US17: Reviews  

---

### 🌱 Low Priority
- US14: Personalized recommendations  
- US15: Wishlist  
- US20: Advanced reports  

